Variable_Descriptions: title of the game
Value_Descriptions: full name of the game

Variable_Descriptions: platform
Value_Descriptions: platform that the game is published

Variable_Descriptions: the release date of the game
Value_Descriptions: specific release date of the game in year-month-date format

Variable_Descriptions: description of the game on the Metacritic page
Value_Descriptions: a paragraph of game descriptions scripted from Metacritic

Variable_Descriptions: score of the game from users
Value_Descriptions: users' score for the game out of 100

Variable_Descriptions: link to the metacritic page of the game
Value_Descriptions: link to the page of the game on metacritic

Variable_Descriptions: number of players
Value_Descriptions:
the number of players that the game support
x player: the game support x players to play
missing: missing information about the number of players that this game supported 
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: number of online players
Value_Descriptions:
the specific number of online playes that the game supported
missing: missing information about the number of players that this game supported 
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: the developer of the the game
Value_Descriptions: specific developers of the game

Variable_Descriptions: generes of the game
Value_Descriptions: genres of the game classified on Metacrtics (specific information about genre are included in the genre dummy varibales)

Variable_Descriptions: ESRB descriptions for the game
Value_Descriptions:
ESRB descriptions of the game
missing: missing information 
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: number of meta reviews that this game received
Value_Descriptions:
number of meta reviews that this game received 
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: number of user reviews that this game received
Value_Descriptions:
number of user reviews that this game received 
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: publishers
Value_Descriptions:
publishers
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: ESRB ratings of the game
Value_Descriptions:
E: Everyone
E10+ : everyone that is above 10
T: Teen (13 and above)
M: Mature (17 and above)
AO: Adults only 18 and above
K-A: kids to adults
missing: missing information 
NA: not avilable/ not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: the ranking of the game for the best game award of the year
Value_Descriptions:
1: the game won the best game award of the year
2-99: the specific rank of the game in best game rankings of the year
100: the game did not win the best game award or included in the ranking of the year or there is no information about this

Variable_Descriptions: the ranking of the game for the most discussed award of the year
Value_Descriptions:
1: the game is the most discussed game of the year
2-99: the specific rank of the game in most discussed game rankings of the year
100: the game are not listed in the ranking of most discussed game of the year or there is no information about this

Variable_Descriptions: the ranking of the game for the most shared award of the year
Value_Descriptions:
1: the game is the most shared game of the year
2-99: the specific rank of the game in most shared game rankings of the year
100: the game did not win the best game award or included in the ranking of the year or there is no information about this

Variable_Descriptions: score for the game from metacritics
Value_Descriptions: users' score for the game out of 100

Variable_Descriptions: company of the game based on the platform
Value_Descriptions: company of the game based on the platform

Variable_Descriptions: number of years from now since the game has beem released
Value_Descriptions: number of years from now since the game has beem released

Value_Descriptions:
TRUE: the game allows multiplayer
FALSE: the game does not allow multiplayer
missing: missing information
NA: not avialable/not applicable

Variable_Descriptions: whether the game support online
Value_Descriptions:

missing: missing information
